title: We’re starting a new band called Magaziine, and this is our first song
description:
The Pomplamoose team and I have been working on this band for 6 months now. To learn more about why we’re creating Magaziine, just watch the vlog at the end of the video!

In the meantime, I have to give a MASSIVE THANK YOU to the core Pomplamoose team for all their incredible, creative work spinning up this project.

Dom, Athena, Chris, Dom (#2), Ben, Lindsay – huge thank you for all the hours of rallying, creativity, brainstorming, visioning, and execution.

Save this song on Spotify: https://spoti.fi/3Th94Ql
Follow us on instagram: https://instagram.com/pomplamoosemusic
Become a patron of our music (to vote on the songs we cover and get merch and stuff like that): http://www.patreon.com/pomplamoose

A cover of "What is Love" by Magaziine, Arielle Kasnetz & Anilee List.
